metadata.name: mainland, Dongling
metadata.description:
Yuanshan County, Su family.



The large hall was filled with arguments.



There were dozens of people standing in the hall, and those who had just spoken were old men over fifty years old. Judging from their clothes, they were all elders.



In the main position, a heavyset middle-aged man is sitting there with a frown, his eyes from time to time glance down to the position of a young man, his eyes are full of helplessness and sigh.
